Phill Lewis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phill_Lewis 0 Phill Lewis (born 1968) is an American actor, director, and comedian, best known for his role as Mr. Moseby on the Disney Channel series The Suite Life of Zack Cody and its spin-off, The Suite Life on Deck. Lewis has also made appearances on popular TV shows such as Lizzie McGuire, Friends, The Wayans Bros and Scrubs.
